6月10日，賈吉擊出一支脫離速率{{convert|121.1|mph}}的全壘打，刷新MLB使用[[Statcast|Statcast]]以來的紀錄。<ref>{{cite web |last=Tasch |first=Justin |url=http://www.nydailynews.com/sports/baseball/yankees/video-aaron-judge-hits-hardest-home-run-recorded-article-1.3238014 |title=VIDEO: Aaron Judge hits hardest home run ever recorded |publisher=NY Daily News |date= |accessdate=June 11, 2017 |archive-date=2021-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413114427/https://www.nydailynews.com/sports/baseball/yankees/video-aaron-judge-hits-hardest-home-run-recorded-article-1.3238014 |dead-url=no }}</ref>隔天他打了一支495英尺的全壘打。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Hoch|first1=Bryan|title=Aaron Judge crushes a 495-foot HR|url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/235754990/aaron-judge-hits-mlbs-longest-hr-in-2017/?topicId=27118122|publisher=MLB|accessdate=June 11, 2017|archive-date=2017-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170729102702/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/235754990/aaron-judge-hits-mlbs-longest-hr-in-2017/?topicId=27118122|dead-url=no}}</ref>賈吉在2017[[美國職棒大聯盟全壘打大賽|全壘打大賽]]三輪一共擊出47支全壘打，贏得冠軍。
